&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_34 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;wtm-85vm1: stat: cannot read file system information for `/mnt/lustre&apos;: Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
first df failed: 1&lt;br/&gt;
